about.summary: A collection of Python utilities for interacting with the Unidata technology stack.

name: siphon
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.4.0" %}

package:
  name: siphon
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: siphon-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/s/siphon/siphon-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: db44fac45257cab97c24edd908ba828607b937224148028b12ef21f1b9b984a1

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python
    - numpy
    - protobuf >=3.0.0a3
    - requests
    - netcdf4
    - enum34  # [py27]

test:
  imports:
    - siphon
    - siphon.cdmr
    - siphon.catalog
    - siphon.ncss
    - siphon.radarserver

about:
  home: https://github.com/Unidata/siphon
  license: MIT
  summary: 'A collection of Python utilities for interacting with the Unidata technology stack.'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf
    - dopplershift
